# 🔐 Advanced Linux Log Analyzer

A Python-based Linux security log analyzer built on Ubuntu using VMware.

This project analyzes `/var/log/auth.log` and detects:

- Failed login attempts
- Invalid user access attempts
- Sudo authentication failures
- Suspicious attack patterns
- Brute force login attempts

## 🛠 Technologies Used

- Python
- Linux (Ubuntu)
- Git & GitHub
- VMware

## 📊 Features

- Security log monitoring
- Automated report generation
- IP-based attack detection
- Username tracking
- Authentication analysis

## 🚀 Run the Project

```bash
sudo python3 analyzer.py
